OL,3,CPolice boss applies to take home
OL,4,Csecretary to court over plans to scrap
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,FThe West Midlands (PCC) has applied
OL,8,Ffor a judicial review against the home
OL,9,Fsecretary's decision to approve the
OL,10,Ftransfer of the powers from the PCC to
OL,11,Fthe mayor.
OL,13,FLabour's Simon Foster had described
OL,14,Fplans to axe the role of PCC after the
OL,15,Fnext mayoral election in May as a
OL,16,F"hostile takeover".
OL,18,FLast week, Conservative West Midlands
OL,19,Fmayor confirmed he and the government
OL,20,Fhad agreed to the transfer of powers
OL,21,Ffollowing a six-week consultation.
