OL,7,FIt would bring the role of West
OL,8,FMidlands mayor closer to the powers of
OL,9,Fother regional mayors like Andy
OL,10,FBurnham, the mayor of Greater
OL,11,FManchester and Sadiq Khan, mayor of
OL,12,FLondon.
OL,14,FThose roles already have power over
OL,15,Fpolice governance.
