OL,7,FAnnouncing his decision to apply for a
OL,8,Fjudicial review, PCC Simon Foster
OL,9,Fsaid: "I have today commenced an
OL,10,Fapplication for judicial review in the
OL,11,FHigh Court against the Secretary of
OL,12,FState for the Home Department,
OL,13,Fchallenging his decision, to approve
OL,14,Fthe hostile takeover of Police and
OL,15,FCrime Commissioner powers by the Mayor.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
