OL,3,CPolice boss applies to take home
OL,4,Csecretary to court over plans to scrap
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,F"This is a matter that is entirely of
OL,8,Fthe Mayor's own making. I have
OL,9,Frepeatedly advised him not to waste
OL,10,Ftaxpayers' money, proceeding with his
OL,11,Fcynical, divisive and undemocratic
OL,12,Fpower grab that is in no-one's
OL,13,Finterests, save that of the Mayor.
OL,15,F"Sadly, the Mayor has refused to
OL,16,Flisten. He has left me with no
OL,17,Falternative, but to proceed with an
OL,18,Fapplication for judicial review."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
