OL,5,Crole
OL,7,FHe added: "The Mayor failed to secure
OL,8,Fa democratic mandate for the transfer
OL,9,Fof PCC powers in 2019. He failed to
OL,10,Fsecure a democratic mandate in 2021.
OL,11,FHis government changed the law to
OL,12,Fremove the need for a democratic
OL,13,Fmandate in 2023.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
