OL,3,CPolice boss applies to take home
OL,4,Csecretary to court over plans to scrap
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,F"The Home Secretary and the Mayor
OL,8,Fadopted an unlawful procedure in
OL,9,FDecember 2023. I had to take legal
OL,10,Faction, to compel them to launch a
OL,11,Flast minute, panic driven, 11th hour
OL,12,Fpublic consultation. The Mayor then
OL,13,Frefused to engage in public debate
OL,14,Fwith me.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
