OL,3,CPolice boss applies to take home
OL,4,Csecretary to court over plans to scrap
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,F"I was refused the opportunity to make
OL,8,Fmy case before the Combined Authority
OL,9,FOverview and Scrutiny Committee. The
OL,10,FHome Secretary and Mayor then failed
OL,11,Fto secure a mandate via the public
OL,12,Fconsultation, because a majority of
OL,13,Fpeople disagreed with the transfer of
OL,14,FPCC powers to the Mayor."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
