OL,3,CPolice boss applies to take home
OL,4,Csecretary to court over plans to scrap
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,FHe continued: "(Andy Street) has
OL,8,Frepeatedly failed to make out his
OL,9,Fcase. Yet, he is persisting with his
OL,10,Fhostile takeover in defiance of local
OL,11,Fdemocracy, contrary to the principles
OL,12,Fof devolution and against the will of
OL,13,Fthe people."
OL,15,FThe government has been criticised for
OL,16,Fannouncing a consultation on the
OL,17,Ftransfer of powers after it had
OL,18,Falready announced the transfer would
OL,19,Ftake place.
