OL,7,FQuestions have also been raised over
OL,8,Fthe consultation, which lasted six
OL,9,Fweeks. Typical consultations can
OL,10,Fnormally last double the length.
OL,12,FMr Foster continued: "Enough is
OL,13,Fenough. As Police and Crime
OL,14,FCommissioner my one and only top
OL,15,Fpriority is preventing, tackling and
OL,16,Freducing crime. I am committed to
OL,17,Fcomplying with my pledge to the
OL,18,Felectorate.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/14
