OL,3,CPolice boss applies to take home
OL,4,Csecretary to court over plans to scrap
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,F"I was elected with a mandate to
OL,8,Fretain a democratically elected and
OL,9,Fdirectly accountable Police and Crime
OL,10,FCommissioner. I repeated that
OL,11,Fcommitment in my Police and Crime
OL,12,FPlan. I intend to fulfil my pledge to
OL,13,Fthe people who elected me.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
