OL,3,CPolice boss applies to take home
OL,4,Csecretary to court over plans to scrap
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,F"The very last thing we need is a
OL,8,FMayor who is in denial of the
OL,9,Fcatastrophic and devastating damage
OL,10,Fhis own government has inflicted on
OL,11,Four police service, executing a
OL,12,Fhostile takeover of policing in the
OL,13,FWest Midlands. It would mean, more
OL,14,Fcuts, more chaos and more crime.
OL,16,F"That is why I will not hesitate to
OL,17,Ftake the action necessary to hold the
OL,18,FHome Secretary and the Mayor to
OL,19,Faccount, to defend democracy, the rule
OL,20,Fof law and the rights of the people I
OL,21,Frepresent.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/14
