OL,3,CPolice boss applies to take home
OL,4,Csecretary to court over plans to scrap
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,F"However, it is not too late. I call
OL,8,Fon the Home Secretary to abandon his
OL,9,Fapproval of the hostile takeover of
OL,10,FPCC powers and I call on the Mayor to
OL,11,Fwithdraw his consent. Have the
OL,12,Fcourage, the integrity and the
OL,13,Fprinciples to put it to the people `
OL,14,Flet the people decide ` who they want
OL,15,Fto represent them as their
OL,16,Fdemocratically elected and directly
OL,17,Faccountable Police and Crime
OL,18,FCommissioner ` on 2 May 2024."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/14
