OL,5,Crole
OL,7,FResponding to the announcement a
OL,8,Fspokesperson for Mr Street said:
OL,9,F"Perhaps if the PCC had put this much
OL,10,Fenergy into his job over the last
OL,11,Fthree years then we wouldn't be in a
OL,12,Fsituation where crime has doubled with
OL,13,Fhis force in special measures.
OL,15,F"We dread to think how much taxpayer
OL,16,Fmoney is being wasted on London
OL,17,Flawyers by the PCC in trying to save
OL,18,Fhis job, money that should be in the
OL,19,FWest Midlands Police budget to be
OL,20,Fspent on frontline officers.
