OL,5,Crole
OL,7,F"To be really clear the Mayor is not
OL,8,Fsubject to this judicial review, and
OL,9,Fhas no intention of backing away from
OL,10,Ftaking the tough steps required to
OL,11,Ftackle the scourge of crime across the
OL,12,FWest Midlands."
OL,14,FThe home secretary has been approached
OL,15,Ffor comment.
